review.description: Man this place is unbelievable, writing as I'm eating! $8 lunch special comes with all the works. The owner even talked to me about his vision for the food today. Really cares about his customers
review.author: Adam K.

review.description: This place is great. Amazing yummy well priced food. The staff is so nice. I got the steak burrito and my boyfriend got the carnitas. Both were excellent. The guac is so yummy. Definitely go!
review.author: Sophie M.
